FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784848712
OL,3,CBodycam captures lifesaving rescue of
OL,4,Cboys swept out to sea
OL,6,FFootage from the Royal National
OL,7,FLifeboat Institution (RNLI) captures
OL,8,Fthe frantic operation during the May
OL,9,Fheatwave, where 10-year-old Subby and
OL,10,FKizza, 12, were left seconds away from
OL,11,Fdrowning as rising tides trapped them
OL,12,Fagainst pier stanchions in Blackpool.
OL,14,FSubby's 21-year-old cousin from
OL,15,FBradford, Ted, is also seen clinging
OL,16,Fto the pier supports in a desperate
OL,17,Fattempt to wade out to the children.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784848712
OL,3,CBodycam captures lifesaving rescue of
OL,4,Cboys swept out to sea
OL,6,FNow, their mother Zully, from Leeds,
OL,7,Fis sharing her "nightmare" alongside
OL,8,Fthe charity for World Drowning
OL,9,FPrevention Day to warn other families
OL,10,Fabout the sudden dangers of coastal
OL,11,Ftides ahead of the summer holidays.
OL,13,FThe family had travelled to the
OL,14,FLancashire seaside town during half-
OL,15,Fterm to celebrate Eid al-Adha. Despite
OL,16,Fchecking tide times online before
OL,17,Fsetting off, Zully says the incoming
OL,18,Ftide trapped the boys quickly.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784848712
OL,3,CBodycam captures lifesaving rescue of
OL,4,Cboys swept out to sea
OL,6,FThe mum-of-four tried to wade into the
OL,7,Fsea to reach them, but was forced back
OL,8,Fby the powerful waves and police
OL,9,Fofficers who arrived at the scene.
OL,11,F"It didn't feel real, it was like I
OL,12,Fwas in some kind of helpless dream ` a
OL,13,Fnightmare," Zully recalled.
OL,15,F"I could see my boy submerged next to
OL,16,Fthe poles of the pier...I was shouting
OL,17,Fat the top of my voice ` we need the
OL,18,Forange boat."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784848712
OL,3,CBodycam captures lifesaving rescue of
OL,4,Cboys swept out to sea
OL,6,FShe added: "I knew he'd cling on if he
OL,7,Fcould hear my voice telling him not to
OL,8,Flet go, but by now the water was
OL,9,Frising fast and I could see him going
OL,10,Funder."
OL,12,FBy the time help arrived, the cousins
OL,13,Fhad been clinging to the structure for
OL,14,F40 minutes, gasping for air as the sea
OL,15,Fwashed over their heads.
OL,17,FA member of the public had dialled
OL,18,F999, prompting the Coastguard to
OL,19,Frequest Blackpool RNLI's volunteer
OL,20,Fcrew`marking their 11th callout in
OL,21,Fjust seven days.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784848712
OL,3,CBodycam captures lifesaving rescue of
OL,4,Cboys swept out to sea
OL,6,FThe RNLI volunteers arrived on scene
OL,7,Fwithin four minutes. Volunteers
OL,8,Fcarefully manoeuvred the lifeboat
OL,9,Falongside the pier stanchions to pull
OL,10,Fboth children out of the water.
OL,12,FDue to the urgency of the situation,
OL,13,Fthe crew rushed the boys straight to
OL,14,Fawaiting paramedics at South Pier,
OL,15,Fwhile a second lifeboat rescued 21-
OL,16,Fyear-old Ted from higher up the pier.
OL,18,FZully, who was unaware the RNLI was a
OL,19,Fvolunteer-run charity before the
OL,20,Frescue, praised the crew who risked
OL,21,Ftheir lives.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784848712
OL,3,CBodycam captures lifesaving rescue of
OL,4,Cboys swept out to sea
OL,6,FShe said: "When I saw Subby coming in
OL,7,Fon that lifeboat and being carried
OL,8,Faway, it was like a miracle. I thought
OL,9,Fhe'd gone. Without the RNLI, I would
OL,10,Fhave lost him. My first boy."
OL,12,FThe RNLI is using the video and the
OL,13,Ffamily's ordeal to promote its Find
OL,14,FYour Float campaign, warning that
OL,15,Fincoming tides can rapidly cut people
OL,16,Foff.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
