OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784848712
OL,3,CBodycam captures lifesaving rescue of
OL,4,Cboys swept out to sea
OL,6,FChris Cousens, RNLI Water Safety Lead,
OL,7,Furged beachgoers to check tide tables,
OL,8,Fpay attention to local safety signs,
OL,9,Fand carry a fully charged mobile phone
OL,10,Fto call 999 for the Coastguard in an
OL,11,Femergency.
OL,13,FIf you unexpectedly find yourself
OL,14,Fstruggling in the water, the RNLI
OL,15,Frecommends the 'Float to Live'
OL,16,Ftechnique:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784848712
OL,3,CBodycam captures lifesaving rescue of
OL,4,Cboys swept out to sea
OL,6,FIf you see someone else in difficulty
OL,7,Fin the water, call 999 or 112 for the
OL,8,FCoastguard, tell the person to float
OL,9,Fon their back, and throw them a
OL,10,Fbuoyant object.
OL,12,FReflecting on the rescue, Zully said:
OL,13,F"The sea can be evil, it doesn't care
OL,14,Fwho you are it just takes you... This
OL,15,Fhappened to the people I love and it
OL,16,Fcould so easily happen to other
OL,17,Ffamilies too."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
